725193f.title: Queens: 31st Avenue - 36th Street
725193f.text:
36-11 and 36-01 31st Avenue, north side, west from 37th
(right) to 36th Streets, showing two apartment houses, of two
units each, the Louvre and the Riviera. 2n the right is the
37th Street side of the Louvre.
MAY BE PEPRODUCED  About 1927
